00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Welcome to the AgentRAG tutorial on semantic search.

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:08,000
In this video, we will explore how to build a RAG pipeline from scratch.

3
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:13,000
First, we need to ingest our documents into the vector store using embeddings.

4
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:17,500
The embedding model converts each text chunk into a dense vector representation.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:23,000
Finally, queries are embedded and matched against stored vectors for retrieval.
